&lt;p&gt;The North Community Therapy team based at Carew House in Bodmin is looking for an enthusiastic and IT literate administrator to join them in supporting the team of clinicians working within the community.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The primary areas of this role include managing referrals, telephone message taking and relaying, ordering of stock and inputting to a number of patient related electronic systems and maintaining databases of information.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant will have administration experience, an ability to learn NHS electronic systems and processes and enjoy all aspects of administration.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a part time job share role offered at 19 hours per week to be worked across Monday, Friday and a Tuesday or Thursday at the successful candidate’s choice.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you are interested and would like to know more, please contact Sarah Smith on 01208 834490&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Thank you for your interest.&lt;/p&gt;
